servinfo.title: Air Cleaner Filter Inspection and Cleaning

ptxt.intxrefpoff: Air Cleaner Filter Removal and Installation

servinfosub.title: Inspection
servinfosub.ptxt: Check filter for dirt. Replace if filter is excessively dirty.

servinfosub.title: Cleaning
servinfosub.ptxt: When cleaning filter, blow off dust by blowing compressed air from air outlet side of filter (i.e., the side facing up when installed in air cleaner case).
